name: Supertech Hill Town Gurgaon
short_description:
Supertech Limited, a trusted name in real estate, launches Supertech Hill Town in Sector - 2, Sohna. 
Book your flat with only 10% down payment and zero EMI till possession. 

Call us on 7053707070 to know the details, avail pre-launch discounts and grab this opportunity to invest and own a property in the project. 

The projectspread over 150 acres and is appropriately situated, next to Gurgaon and is well connected to all residential, commercial and industrial hubs of Delhi, Noida and DMIC regions such as Neemrana, Manesar and Ghiloth. The presence of renowned and established hotels, schools, hospitals, universities, business centers and other economic generators around the project site make it fit not only for a home but also as a prospective investment. The proposed connectivity enhancements of the region, through roads and metro will certainly enhance the probable returns on your investment.

Book now at prices as low as INR 4,250/Sqft.
